These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, coach, scientist
1. the coach is on the far left##1
2. the project-manager is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | coach | scientist | project-manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, engineer, social-worker
1. the social-worker is on the far right##1
2. the pilot is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | pilot | engineer | social-worker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | traveling | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: german, american, indian
1. the american is on the far right##1
2. the american is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | german | indian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, soy-milk
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | fanta | coffee | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike, ship
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | ship | quad-bike | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, spy, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | crime | spy |

